                            <br> <br>
                            <blockquote>“For I can see in the midst of death, life persists, in the midst of untruth, truth persists, in the midst of darkness light persists.” --- Mahatma Gandhi</blockquote>

                            This quote by the Father of the Indian Nation perfectly describes the work that is being carried out by NGOs &amp; citizens to help bring relief &amp; joy to the darkest corners of India. The Bangalore chapter of the NGO, Liter of Light, is one such organisation
                            that has made great strides in the past and continues to fight for this noble cause.
                        </div>
                    </div>
