                                <br><br> Gurunathan, takes care of his daughter, Sashi, all by himself. He takes her with him to the fields. Sashi plays in the field while her father works all day. But as the sun sets , and the fields become dark, Sashi
                                no longer can see her father, and this frightens her. Now with the night light, Gurunathan can continue to work and Sashi will no longer be frightened.<br><br>
                                <div style="text-align:center;">
